product_name: Open Country Clean-A-Screen for FD-75SK Dehydrator - Set of 2
long_description: For use with the Open Country 700-Watt FD-75SK food dehydrator (sold separately), the Clean-A-Screen is perfect for drying small items such as spices and herbs. Just place the screen on top of the dehydrator's plastic tray to prevent small items from falling through the spokes of the tray. Open Country Clean-A-Screen is reusable. Package includes 2 Clean-A-Screens.
